1a:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-7 text-foreground/90","children":["That's the whole philosophy: automate the hygiene so it's impossible to forget, and\nspend the freed attention on the writing only a human with real experience can produce.\nThe check makes sure this very post has a canonical URL, an Article JSON-LD node, an OG\ncard, and a sitemap entry. Whether it's worth citing is on us — and on the folder\nstructure that made ",["$","a",null,{"className":"font-medium text-primary underline underline-offset-4","href":"/apps-services-libs","children":"adding this blog a three-line change"}],"."]}]
